=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 13, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qgx1665702538490.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qgx1665702538490.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qgx1665702538490.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qgx1665702538490\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Restores the initial values of a field's syntax properties.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__topic_d126392e1_d126393e1_d126394e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__p_d126395e1_d126396e1_d126397e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldObject</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">clearSyntaxProperties()</span>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__section_w787ab1b5b3_w788ab1b5_w789ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865630e64\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__section_w790ab1b5b5_w791ab1b5_w792ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865630e73\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"shk1665703139073.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" title=\"Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a></code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__section_w793ab1b5b7_w794ab1b5_w795ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865630e94\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__p_d126413e1_d126414e1_d126415e1\">The initial values of a DSP field's widget properties\n        can be set in the Define (Component) Field Properties dialog, or they can be set in Proc\n        using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldsyntax</span>. The can be retrieved in JavaScript using the\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getDeclarativeSyntax</span> function.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__p_d126416e1_d126417e1_d126418e1\">Once the DSP is loaded, the values of these properties\n        can be dynamically changed in the browser using the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setSyntaxProperty</span> and\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setSyntaxProperties</span> API functions.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qgx1665702538490__p_d126419e1_d126420e1_d126421e1\">You can use the\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">clearSyntaxProperties</span> function to reset the field's syntax properties\n        to their initial values.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjg1714304600909.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Field Syntax Codes</a><p>Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmv1714306853376.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>clearSyntaxProperty()</a><p>Restores the initial value of the specified syntax property.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zpb1714306631479.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getSyntaxProperties()</a><p>Retrieves field syntax properties that were set in the browser (using the setSyntaxProperty or setSyntaxProperties functions).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/otb1714306145328.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setSyntaxProperties()</a><p>Sets multiple syntax properties for a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Field</a><p>The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531253\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531253\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "clearSyntaxProperties() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 13, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Restores the initial values of a field's syntax properties. FieldObject . clearSyntaxProperties() Arguments None Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Description The initial values of a DSP field's widget properties can be set in the Define (Component) Field Properties dialog, or they can be set in Proc using $fieldsyntax . The can be retrieved in JavaScript using the getDeclarativeSyntax function. Once the DSP is loaded, the values of these properties can be dynamically changed in the browser using the setSyntaxProperty and setSyntaxProperties API functions. You can use the clearSyntaxProperties function to reset the field's syntax properties to their initial values. Related Links Field Syntax Codes Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only. clearSyntaxProperty() Restores the initial value of the specified syntax property. getSyntaxProperties() Retrieves field syntax properties that were set in the browser (using the setSyntaxProperty or setSyntaxProperties functions). setSyntaxProperties() Sets multiple syntax properties for a field. uniface.Field The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}